, and to the Barmakids’ hospital in Baghdad, where Sanskrit medical texts were translated and transmitted.</note></biblStruct><bibl type="formatted" subtype="bibliography" resp="https://www.zotero.org/styles/chicago-note-bibliography-17th-edition">
